      "description": "Up for sale is a 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera (997.1), a quintessential driver's machine featuring the 3.6L flat-six M96 powerplant and a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. This example maintains excellent mechanical integrity, with the VarioCam Plus system providing a broad, linear power band and the factory-spec multi-link rear suspension offering precise turn-in. The chassis is rigid and free of excessive play, while the braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers for consistent thermal management. Recent preventative maintenance includes a clutch replacement and a full cooling system flush. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping indicative of spirited road use, the drivetrain remains in peak operating condition, delivering the visceral, analog feedback these hydraulic-steering Porsches are known for.",
